{"tid":1922591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎 新增兩確診 5天內13宗輸入個案","createTime":"2020-03-12T15:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T04:08:05.000Z","uid":249924,"like":77,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"fd58018891fc26320cb6897ad203613de7117fee","tid":1922591,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T15:52:13.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎病例每日遞增，現時本港共有131宗確診個案及1宗疑似個案。由3月8日開始，5日內至今已有13宗輸入個案，及2宗相關密切接觸者個案。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心晚上公佈一宗確診個案，患者是一名31歲男子，居於西寧街35號西寧閣，他3月8日乘坐國泰航班CX930由馬尼拉飛抵本港，然後坐的士回住所。他3月11日曾到過香港大學明華綜合大樓；3月12日則曾到瑪麗醫院，同日坐的士由醫院回家；其後他證實確診感染武漢肺炎，安排到屯門醫院接受治療。此外，第130號女患者的37歲丈夫亦已確診，他2月29日與妻子和歲半大的男嬰，乘搭CX250由英國倫敦返港，昨日入院後初步檢測呈陽性。兩人的1歲5個月大男嬰有鼻水，目前在瑪嘉烈醫院治療。"},{"pid":"298d65b706b524749716d3e22a031ec1c2f5a535","tid":1922591,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"Source : 蘋果"},{"pid":"7425e0ee5c50d36b388f8d52ea16637c0290af7f","tid":1922591,"uid":286626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"賓賓國睇個數唔多嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee14cdab1de086c177c6572d2e51ad5cac10d1a","tid":1922591,"uid":249924,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"7425e0ee5c50d36b388f8d52ea16637c0290af7f","tid":1922591,"uid":286626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T15:54:10.000Z","msg":"賓賓國睇個數唔多嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"冇錢check 姐"},{"pid":"3a86e70d9587bfa08b6c669950cf26e8a4af1425","tid":1922591,"uid":249924,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7425e0ee5c50d36b388f8d52ea16637c0290af7f","tid":1922591,"uid":286626,"like":4,"d